title: Wright Thumbs Up Aina’s Display Vs Liverpool
text: Arsenal legend Ian Wright has showered encomium on Ola Aina for his impressive performance in Nottingham Forest’s victory over Liverpool. Nuno Espirito Santo’s side defeated Liverpool 1-0 at the Anfield last Saturday with Callum Hudson-Odoi netting the winning goal 18 minutes from time. It was the Tricky Trees first victory at the Anfield in 55 years. Aina played a crucial role in Forest’s victory neutralising their dangerous winger Luis Diaz. The 27-year-old has featured in all Nottingham Forest’s four league games this season. Nottingham Forest are unbeaten so far in the Premier League this season. By Adeboye Amosu Got what it Takes?
